	dprr:hasNoteText "Aedile? by 39. See MRR 2.466, 488. The tribe is attested as # in the SC de Panamareis. See Sherk, RDGE no. 27, 158-162; Syme, Historia 13, 1964, 113; Wiseman, NM 216, no. 87.\n" .
